    <item>
      <title>美联储维持利率不变，华尔街降息梦想仍需等待</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/wall-street-s-rate-cut-dreams-have-to-wait-as-fed-stays-on-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储 (FED) 预计 2024 年仅降息一次，交易员们希望央行能更积极地降低借贷成本，华尔街周三面临现实的考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/wall-street-s-rate-cut-dreams-have-to-wait-as-fed-stays-on-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
